We, Forfend Security are eager to make your life safer, easier and smarter. After several years work, we finally make it happen. Our safe box could work with our gateway , APP, Amazon Alexa. Remote control and alarm system will protect you and your property better. Hope our products meet all your expectation. If you have any question or suggestion, feel free to contact us through our APP.

Users could open safe, cancel alarm by using Amazon Alexa. To open the safe, you could use any passwords that registered in your safe.

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "FORFEND" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on our devices and connect them with “FORFEND” app;
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with "FORFEND" App. So if you rename a safe “bedroom safe”, then Echo will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 9;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "ForfendSecuritySkill";
(7). Click Enable skill of "ForfendSecuritySkill", then input your account username and password on the linking page;
(8). Talk to Echo "“Alexa,discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands ForfendSecuritySkill has:

Safe:
1. Alexa, open Forfend Security, unlock bedroom safe
2. Alexa, open Forfend Security, activate tamper alarm of bedroom safe / activate bedroom safe
3. Alexa, open Forfend Security, deactivate tamper alarm of bedroom safe / deactivate bedroom safe
4. Alexa, open Forfend Security, turn off the alarm
5. Alexa, open Forfend Security, high performance mode for bedroom safe / high for bedroom safe
6. Alexa, open Forfend Security, low power mode for bedroom safe / low for bedroom safe
